Ø	Step 1
Contact the partner who placed the order and ask if the End-User has an active DRM Account Number with DIGI. 

(A). If, YES, the partner needs the following 3 items from the E/U – you need all 3 to correct the order.
•	DRM Acct#
•	Name of DRM Administrator (person who manages the DRM and/or hardware).
•	Email address for the Administrator.

(B). If NO, the partner needs the following 2 items from the E/U – you need both items to correct the order.
•	NAME and EMAIL of the DRM Administrator


Ø	Step 2
Once you have the needed info from the Partner (info from A OR B); correct the returned order by entering the info in the SHIPBOL field of the order. 

Ø	Step 3
Requeue the order and a new VPO will be assigned. 

NEED HELP? QUESTIONS? Contact the DIGI BDE > kim.barnett@tdsynnex.com
